-- 17 JAN --
Had some trouble installing FLash for firefox. Turns out the issue was just the permission for the .so file.
Follow instructions here:
https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/redhat-linux-yum-install-flash-player-for-firefox/

tar -zxvf flash_player_npapi_linux.x86_64.tar.gz
sudo cp libflashplayer.so /usr/lib64/mozilla/plugins/
sudo chmod 0755 /usr/lib64/mozilla/plugins/libflashplayer.so